caption.text:
-A traditional Reog dancer-

Different from the East Java version, the Reog of Boyolali (Central Java) is a unique dance performed once a year to celebrate the Eid Mubarak. As the music goes faster, the dancers enter a state of trance, making them tireless and more agile in moving.

caption.text:
Nelumbo nucifera, or commonly known as the Lotus flower, is a sacred flower to religions in Asia, mostly Hindu and Buddha. To the Hindus, lotus is a representation of Vishnu as Padmanabha. To the Buddhist it represents purity of the body, speech, and mind, as if floating above the muddy waters of attachment and desire.¬†Due to the fascination of its beauty, lotuses are often used in poems and songs to represent elegance, beauty, perfection, purity and grace.

Stumbled upon this photo recently. One of the earliest photographs I took since I developed an interest in photography. #tbt #photography #lotus #flower #beauty #canon #500d
